Former German chancellor Gerhard Schr√∂der is visiting Moscow for talks with Russian President Vladimir Putin, according to Politico.

Citing sources familiar with the matter, the outlet said that Schr√∂der is hoping to persuade Putin to end the war in Ukraine.

